  <synopsis><code mime="text/x-gjs">
function add_snippet(snippet: <link xref="Cogl.Snippet">Cogl.Snippet</link>): void {
    // Gjs wrapper for cogl_pipeline_add_snippet()
}
  </code></synopsis>
  <p>Adds a shader snippet to <code>pipeline</code>. The snippet will wrap around or
replace some part of the pipeline as defined by the hook point in
<code>snippet</code>. Note that some hook points are specific to a layer and
must be added with <link xref="Cogl.Pipeline.add_layer_snippet"/> instead.</p>
  <p>Since 1.10</p>
